2004-10-20  Tony Graham  <tonygraham@users.sourceforge.net>

	* === Released 0.3.0 ===

	* configure.ac: Changed to refer to 'GNOME Print backend of
	xmlroff', not PangoPDF.

	* NEWS: Updated for libfo-examples 0.3.0.

	* gmodule-area-tree.c, xmlroff-basic.c, xmlroff-gmodule.c,
	xmlroff-libfo.c, xmlroff-text-tree.c, xmlroff-text-tree2.c:
	Removed '-compress' param.  Improved initial comments.  Stopped
	some compiler warnings.

	* README: Added xmlroff-gmodule usage examples.  Added titles.

2004-10-12  Tony Graham  <tonygraham@users.sourceforge.net>

	* gmodule-area-tree.c, xmlroff-gmodule.c, xmlroff-libfo.c,
	xmlroff-text-tree.c, xmlroff-text-tree2.c: Expunged mentions of
	PDFlib.

	* configure.ac: Updated for changes from libfo-0.3 to libfo-0.3,
	pangopdf to pangoxsl.

2004-06-02  Tony Graham  <tonygraham@users.sourceforge.net>

	* === Released 0.2.7 ===

	* README: Updated for xmlroff-text-tree, xmlroff-text-tree2,
	xmlroff-gmodule, and gmodule-area-tree.

	* NEWS: Updated for 0.2.7.

	* xmlroff-text-tree.c: Removed a cast to stop a compiler warning.

	* configure.ac: Added check for gmodule-2.0.

	* autogen.sh: Changed project name to 'libfo-examples'.

	* Makefile.am: Added items for xmlroff-gmodule,
	xmlroff-text-tree2, and gmodule-area-tree.

	* gmodule-area-tree.c, xmlroff-gmodule.c: Demonstration of a
	separate loadable module that shows area tree.

	* xmlroff-text-tree2.c: Displays area tree using on
	g_object_get_property() to access tree.

2004-05-17  Tony Graham  <tonygraham@users.sourceforge.net>

	* configure.ac: Changed long description.  Upped version to 0.2.7.
	Added check for GTK+ and for libfo backends.

	* autogen.sh: Added support for libtool 1.5*.

	* Makefile.am, xmlroff-text-tree.c: Added xmlroff-text-tree.c to
	demonstrate accessing FO tree as GObjects.

	* README: Modified project name, changed homepage to
	http://www.xmlroff.org/.

2003-07-24  Tony Graham  <tonygraham@users.sourceforge.net>

	* xmlroff-libfo.c: Changed to default to gp backend.  Updated
	fo_xsl_formatter unref style.

2003-07-18  Tony Graham  <tonygraham@users.sourceforge.net>

	* README: Updated for re-inclusion of xmlroff-libfo.

	* xmlroff-libfo.c: Updated to use fo_xsl_formatter_draw() instead
	of fo_area_to_pdf().

	* Makefile.am: Added xmlroff-libfo back as Make target.

2003-07-08  Tony Graham  <tonygraham@users.sourceforge.net>

	* === Released 0.2.3.1 ===

	* configure.ac: Increased version number to 0.2.3.1. since
	xmlroff-libfo.c added to dist.

	* Makefile.am: Corrected G_LOG_DOMAIN symbol to 'libfo-examples'.

2003-07-07  Tony Graham  <tonygraham@users.sourceforge.net>

	* autogen.sh, configure.ac: Corrected project name to
	'libfo-examples' since now separate project.

	* Makefile.am: Updated for use as separate project not in
	subdirectory of xmlroff project.

	* xmlroff-libfo.c: Updated to match real 'xmlroff' but can't
	compile in absence of some headers.

	* xmlroff-basic.c, xmlroff-init2.c: Updated initial comment,
	stopped allowing one-dash parameters.

	* AUTHORS, autogen.sh, ChangeLog, configure.ac, COPYING, NEWS,
	README: New files.

